                <p>The most significant upgrade is, of course, the engine. The Karizma XMR 250 is expected to be powered by a<span class="font-weight-700"> new 250cc, Single-Cylinder, Liquid-Cooled, DOHC (Double Overhead Camshaft) </span>engine. The DOHC setup is a premium feature that allows for more precise valve control, which typically translates to better performance across the rev band and higher redline limits.</p>
